### 注册 v1
POST http://localhost:18007/prompts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "greeting",
  "version": "v1",
  "template": "你好，我是{assistant_name}，很高兴为你服务。"
}

### 注册 v2
POST http://localhost:18007/prompts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "greeting",
  "version": "v2",
  "template": "Hi～我是{assistant_name}，有什么可以帮你？"
}

### 列出版本
GET http://localhost:18007/prompts/greeting

### 查询指定版本
GET http://localhost:18007/prompts/greeting/v1

### 仅渲染
POST http://localhost:18007/prompts/greeting/v1/render
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "params": {"assistant_name": "小艾"}
}

### 渲染并调用模型
POST http://localhost:18007/prompts/greeting/v1/invoke
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "params": {"assistant_name": "小艾"}
}
